Package context.arch.handler


Interface Summary
AsyncServiceHandler This empty interface allows the ServiceHandlers class to keep track of servic handlers.
Handler This empty interface allows the Handlers class to keep track of handlers.
 

Class Summary
AsyncServiceHandlerInfo This class acts as a container for handler info.
AsyncServiceHandlers This class maintains a list of asynchronous service handlers, allows additions and removals of individual handlers.
HandlerInfo This class acts as a container for handler info.
Handlers This class maintains a list of context widget handlers, allows additions and removals of individual handlers.
